			<span class="by"><span class="byby">by </span><a rel="nofollow" href="//slashdot.org/~EmoryM">EmoryM</a>  <span class="uid"><a rel="nofollow" href="//slashdot.org/~EmoryM">( 2726097 )</a></span></a></span><span class="writes" style="display:none"> writes:</span> 
			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_64676414"></span>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64676414">If Jim Varney was alive and a screenplay was written for "Ernest Saves The President," and everyone involved in Trump's protection was being portrayed as comically inept, and it was revealed to be a plot by nefarious forces to allow Trump to be shot - that the worst people were put into key positions - and Ernest did in fact save the President...  well, I'm not sure where I was going with this anymore, I think we watched that except without Ernest.  Luckily Trump turned his head.</div>
